OL,3,CInvestigation continues into death of
OL,4,Cteenager in river during heatwave
OL,6,FInvestigations are continuing into the
OL,7,Fdeath of a fourteen-year-old boy who
OL,8,Fgot into difficulty in the River
OL,9,FThames.
OL,11,FBaltazar Da Costa entered the water
OL,12,Fnear Donnington Bridge in Oxford on
OL,13,F27th May during the heatwave.
OL,15,FAt the opening of an inquest today
OL,16,F(10th June), the coroner, Darren
OL,17,FSalter, said a doctor from the air
OL,18,Fambulance confirmed Baltazar's death
OL,19,Fat just after 7pm.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
