OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781179881
OL,3,CInvestigation continues into death of
OL,4,Cteenager in river during heatwave
OL,6,FWhile the exact cause of Baltazar's
OL,7,Fdeath remains unknown pending a report
OL,8,Ffrom the pathologist, the coroner said
OL,9,Fhe believed it is likely Baltazar
OL,10,Fdrowned.
OL,12,FThe inquest was then adjourned until
OL,13,F21st September.
OL,15,FThe inquest heard Baltazar was born in
OL,16,FEast Timor in South-East Asia, but
OL,17,Flived in Stanford-in-the-Vale near
OL,18,FFaringdon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
