PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781179881
OL,3,CInvestigation continues into death of
OL,4,Cteenager in river during heatwave
OL,6,FHis parents, referred to in court as
OL,7,FPedro and Manuela, are reported to
OL,8,Fhave warned other families through the
OL,9,FEast Timor community about the dangers
OL,10,Fof open water.
OL,12,FTheir warning comes amid growing calls
OL,13,Ffor greater awareness around water
OL,14,Fsafety nationwide.
OL,16,FThe day before Baltazar died in
OL,17,FOxford, Samuel Murphy, who was also
OL,18,F14, died at Hawley Lake near
OL,19,FBlackwater in Surrey.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
