CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781179881
OL,3,CInvestigation continues into death of
OL,4,Cteenager in river during heatwave
OL,6,FThe deaths have prompted an urgent
OL,7,Fcall to action by the Hampshire MP,
OL,8,FDarren Paffey, the chair of the all-
OL,9,Fparliamentary group on water safety
OL,10,Feducation.
OL,12,FDarren Paffey MP addressed the issue
OL,13,Fof water safety in Parliament.
OL,15,FPaffey believes many of these deaths
OL,16,Fwere 'highly preventable' and wants
OL,17,Ffurther Government action to raise
OL,18,Fawareness particularly before the
OL,19,Fsummer holidays.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
