PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781179881
OL,3,CInvestigation continues into death of
OL,4,Cteenager in river during heatwave
OL,6,F''196 children drowned in open water
OL,7,Fin the last six years alone," Paffey
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"That's a classroom full full of
OL,11,Fchildren every year. But what we saw
OL,12,Fduring the recent heatwave is
OL,13,Fparticularly shocking."
OL,15,FHe added: "We now know that in just
OL,16,Fover a week, 19 people are confirmed
OL,17,Fto have died, and the vast majority of
OL,18,Fthose, 13, were children."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
